House-2.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\" data-cfsrc=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/DWR-Boutique-Experimential-Rental-Home-Wave-House-2-810x458.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThis isn’t your average rental home. The newly unveiled \u003ca href=\"https://boutique-homes.com/property/the-desert-wave\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener external noreferrer\" data-wpel-link=\"external\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eDWR x Boutique Rental Home\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/a\u003e invites guests to experience the intersection of architecture, furniture, and fashion in an intimate, immersive setting. It marks the first time that DWR has launched an experiential rental home – an innovative step that brings modern design to life in a tangible, livable way.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=576349\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-576349\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/DWR-Boutique-Experimential-Rental-Home-Wave-House-3-810x1063.jpg\" alt=\"A mid-century modern living room with a striped sofa and armchair, wooden coffee table, side tables, beige rug, and floor-to-ceiling windows with patterned curtains.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1063\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/DWR-Boutique-Experimential-Rental-Home-Wave-House-3-810x1063.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/DWR-Boutique-Experimential-Rental-Home-Wave-House-3-800x1050.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/DWR-Boutique-Experimential-Rental-Home-Wave-House-3-768x1008.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/DWR-Boutique-Experimential-Rental-Home-Wave-House-3-1170x1536.jpg 1170w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/DWR-Boutique-Experimential-Rental-Home-Wave-House-3.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\" data-cfsrc=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/DWR-Boutique-Experimential-Rental-Home-Wave-House-3-810x1063.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe Wave House, originally constructed in 1955 by architect Walter S. White, is a striking example of organic modernism. Its curved roof – an architectural gesture mirroring the San Jacinto Mountains – sets it apart from the many mid-century homes scattered across the Coachella Valley. Initially created as both a residence and a creative studio for artist Miles C. Bates, the home quickly became a cultural escape for artists and thinkers of the era.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=576350\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-576350\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/DWR-Boutique-Experimential-Rental-Home-Wave-House-4-810x1013.jpg\" alt=\"Mid-century modern interior with a striped sofa, wooden sideboard, record player, maroon lamp, vase with branches, and a textured cream wall with geometric accents.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1013\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/DWR-Boutique-Experimential-Rental-Home-Wave-House-4-810x1013.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/DWR-Boutique-Experimential-Rental-Home-Wave-House-4-800x1000.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/DWR-Boutique-Experimential-Rental-Home-Wave-House-4-768x960.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/DWR-Boutique-Experimential-Rental-Home-Wave-House-4-1229x1536.jpg 1229w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/DWR-Boutique-Experimential-Rental-Home-Wave-House-4.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\" data-cfsrc=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/DWR-Boutique-Experimential-Rental-Home-Wave-House-4-810x1013.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eAfter a meticulous restoration by \u003ca href=\"https://staynerarchitects.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener external noreferrer\" data-wpel-link=\"external\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eStayner Architects\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/a\u003e, the house was reopened to the public in 2020, reclaiming its place as a Palm Desert landmark. Today, it stands not only on the National Register of Historic Places but also as a city-designated historical site. With the latest transformation, it enters a new chapter – one where guests can step directly into a curated environment where the lines between home, gallery, and showroom blur.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=576351\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-576351\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/DWR-Boutique-Experimential-Rental-Home-Wave-House-5-810x1063.jpg\" alt=\"A close-up view of an upholstered chair with a striped fabric pattern in shades of green, brown, black, and white.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1063\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/DWR-Boutique-Experimential-Rental-Home-Wave-House-5-810x1063.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/DWR-Boutique-Experimential-Rental-Home-Wave-House-5-800x1050.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/DWR-Boutique-Experimential-Rental-Home-Wave-House-5-768x1008.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/DWR-Boutique-Experimential-Rental-Home-Wave-House-5-1170x1536.jpg 1170w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/DWR-Boutique-Experimential-Rental-Home-Wave-House-5.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\" data-cfsrc=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/DWR-Boutique-Experimential-Rental-Home-Wave-House-5-810x1063.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe project coincides with the launch of \u003cstrong\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.dwr.com/paul-smith-maharam?lang=en_US\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener external noreferrer\" data-wpel-link=\"external\"\u003eDWR Presents: The Paul Smith Collection\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/strong\u003e, a vibrant fusion of iconic modern furniture and the renowned Br