que-Experimential-Rental-Home-Wave-House-6-1170x1536.jpg 1170w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/DWR-Boutique-Experimential-Rental-Home-Wave-House-6.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\" data-cfsrc=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/DWR-Boutique-Experimential-Rental-Home-Wave-House-6-810x1063.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eFrom bold plaids and textured stripes to energetic polka dots, Paul Smith’s signature aesthetic is on full display, giving the home a distinctive character that reflects both its heritage and its evolution. The result is a dialogue between two design eras, brought together by a shared commitment to craft, quality, and storytelling.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=576353\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-576353\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/DWR-Boutique-Experimential-Rental-Home-Wave-House-6m-810x1063.jpg\" alt=\"A green booklet with \u0026#34;PAUL SMITH\u0026#34; written on it rests on a multicolored striped fabric surface.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1063\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/DWR-Boutique-Experimential-Rental-Home-Wave-House-6m-810x1063.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/DWR-Boutique-Experimential-Rental-Home-Wave-House-6m-800x1050.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/DWR-Boutique-Experimential-Rental-Home-Wave-House-6m-768x1008.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/DWR-Boutique-Experimential-Rental-Home-Wave-House-6m-1170x1536.jpg 1170w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/DWR-Boutique-Experimential-Rental-Home-Wave-House-6m.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\" data-cfsrc=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/DWR-Boutique-Experimential-Rental-Home-Wave-House-6m-810x1063.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/