d two pendant lights above a white bedside table.\" width=\"810\" height=\"540\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/DWR-Boutique-Experimential-Rental-Home-Wave-House-8-810x540.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/DWR-Boutique-Experimential-Rental-Home-Wave-House-8-800x533.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/DWR-Boutique-Experimential-Rental-Home-Wave-House-8-768x512.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/DWR-Boutique-Experimential-Rental-Home-Wave-House-8.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\" data-cfsrc=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/DWR-Boutique-Experimential-Rental-Home-Wave-House-8-810x540.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=576356\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-576356\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/DWR-Boutique-Experimential-Rental-Home-Wave-House-9-810x532.jpg\" alt=\"A mid-century modern bedroom with a wooden ceiling, an upholstered bed, pendant lights, orange curtains, and an open door, featuring warm, earthy tones and minimalist decor.\" width=\"810\" height=\"532\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/DWR-Boutique-Experimential-Rental-Home-Wave-House-9-810x532.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/DWR-Boutique-Experimential-Rental-Home-Wave-House-9-800x525.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/DWR-Boutique-Experimential-Rental-Home-Wave-House-9-768x504.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/DWR-Boutique-Experimential-Rental-Home-Wave-House-9-385x252.jpg 385w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/DWR-Boutique-Experimential-Rental-Home-Wave-House-9.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\" data-cfsrc=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/DWR-Boutique-Experimential-Rental-Home-Wave-House-9-810x532.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eBy teaming up with Boutique – a vacation rental platform known for its design-centric properties around the globe – DWR ensures that this vision extends beyond aesthetics. Guests are not just observers; they are participants in a fully designed experience. Each room, each piece of furniture, each accent has been chosen not just to look beautiful, but to feel meaningful in use.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=576357\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-576357\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/DWR-Boutique-Experimential-Rental-Home-Wave-House-10-810x1013.jpg\" alt=\"A wooden desk with drawers, a modern white chair, a black desk lamp, and orange curtains in a room with a wood ceiling and high windows.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1013\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/DWR-Boutique-Experimential-Rental-Home-Wave-House-10-810x1013.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/DWR-Boutique-Experimential-Rental-Home-Wave-House-10-800x1000.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/DWR-Boutique-Experimential-Rental-Home-Wave-House-10-768x960.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/DWR-Boutique-Experimential-Rental-Home-Wave-House-10-1229x1536.jpg 1229w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/DWR-Boutique-Experimential-Rental-Home-Wave-House-10.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\" data-cfsrc=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/DWR-Boutique-Experimential-Rental-Home-Wave-House-10-810x1013.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eFor Boutique, whose global portfolio includes over 1,500 architecturally significant homes, the collaboration is a natural extension of their mission to elevate travel through great design. “We’ve always believed that where you stay should be as inspiring as where you go,” says Marc Blazer, CEO and Co-Founder of Boutique. “Partnering with DWR, who shares our passion for thoughtful, expressive design, allows us to create a space where travelers can connect with creativity on a deeper level.”\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=576358\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-576358\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/DWR-Boutique-Experimential-Rental-Home-Wave-House-11-810x532.jpg\" alt=\"A modern room with glass sliding doors, orange walls, and beige curtains, showing a bed, armchair, tulips on a table, and outdoor gravel pathway.\" width=\"810\" height=\"532\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/DWR-Boutique-Experimential-Rental-Home-Wave-House-11-810x532.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/DWR-Boutique-Experimential-Rental-Home-Wave-House-11-800x525.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/DWR-Boutique-Experimential-Rental-Home-Wave-House-11-768x504.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/DWR-Boutique-Experimential-Rental-Home-Wave-House-11-385x252.jpg 385w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/DWR-Boutique-Experimential-Rental-Home-Wave-House-11.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\" data-cfsrc=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/DWR-Boutique-Experimential-Rental-Home-Wave-House-11-810x532.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=576359\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-576359\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/DWR-Boutique-Experimential-Rental-Home-Wave-House-12-810x1013.jpg\" alt=\"A modern bathroom with glass walls overlooks a small enclosed desert garden featuring various cacti and succulents. A striped towel hangs on the wall beside a small wooden stool.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1013\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/DWR-Boutique-Experimential-Rental-Home-Wave-House-12-810x1013.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/DWR-Boutique-Experimential-Rental-Home-Wave-House-12-800x1000.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/DWR-Boutique-Experimential-Rental-Home-Wave-House-12-768x960.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/DWR-Boutique-Experimential-Rental-Home-Wave-House-12-1229x1536.jpg 1229w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/DWR-Boutique-Experimential-Rental-Home-Wave-House-12.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\" data-cfsrc=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/DWR-Boutique-Experimential-Rental-Home-Wave-House-12-810x1013.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe interior of the Wave House showcases the synergy between comfort and curation. Outdoors, sleek furnishings are set against the sculptural desert landscape, enhancing the property’s harmony with nature. Inside, bedrooms are wrapped in soft, layered textiles, offering tactile comfort alongside visual delight. Every detail – down to the placement of objects and the integration of color – has been considered to reflect the ethos of both brands.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=576360\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-576360\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/DWR-Boutique-Experimential-Rental-Home-Wave-House-13-810x1013.jpg\" alt=\"Glass-walled shower with blue mosaic tiles, modern fixtures, and a view of an outdoor area with rocks and a cactus plant.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1013\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/DWR-Boutique-Experimential-Rental-Home-Wave-House-13-810x1013.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/DWR-Boutique-Experimential-Rental-Home-Wave-House-13-800x1000.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/DWR-Boutique-Experimential-Rental-Home-Wave-House-13-768x960.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/DWR-Boutique-Experimential-Rental-Home-Wave-House-13-1229x1536.jpg 1229w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/DWR-Boutique-Experimential-Rental-Home-Wave-House-13.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\" data-cfsrc=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/DWR-Boutique-Experimential-Rental-Home-Wave-House-13-810x1013.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=576361\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-576361\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/DWR-Boutique-Experimential-Rental-Home-Wave-House-14-810x532.jpg\" alt=\"A modern house with a wavy roof, glass walls, and a patio featuring outdoor chairs and a table, surrounded by gravel, palm trees, and a red privacy wall.\" width=\"810\" height=\"532\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/DWR-Boutique-Experimential-Rental-Home-Wave-House-14-810x532.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/DWR-Boutique-Experimential-Rental-Home-Wave-House-14-800x525.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/DWR-Boutique-Experimential-Rental-Home-Wave-House-14-768x504.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/DWR-Boutique-Experimential-Rental-Home-Wave-House-14-385x252.jpg 385w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/DWR-Boutique-Experimential-Rental-Home-Wave-House-14.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\" data-cfsrc=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/DWR-Boutique-Experimential-Rental-Home-Wave-House-14-810x532.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThis initiative signals a shift in how brands like DWR think about customer engagement. Rather than limit interactions to retail environments, they’re offering design lovers a chance to live with the pieces, to understand their proportions, materials, and moods in the context of daily life. It’s about putting modern design within reach – quite literally.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=576362\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-576362\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/DWR-Boutique-Experimential-Rental-Home-Wave-House-15-810x532.jpg\" alt=\"Poolside area with two lounge chairs, a white umbrella, and a modern house with large glass windows in the background. Desert landscaping surrounds the seating area.\" width=\"810\" height=\"532\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/DWR-Boutique-Experimential-Rental-Home-Wave-House-15-810x532.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/DWR-Boutique-Experimential-Rental-Home-Wave-House-15-800x525.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/DWR-Boutique-Experimential-Rental-Home-Wave-House-15-768x504.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/DWR-Boutique-Experimential-Rental-Home-Wave-House-15-385x252.jpg 385w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/DWR-Boutique-Experimential-Rental-Home-Wave-House-15.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\" data-cfsrc=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/DWR-Boutique-Experimential-Rental-Home-Wave-House-15-810x532.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=576364\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-576364\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/DWR-Boutique-Experimential-Rental-Home-Wave-House-17-810x608.jpg\" alt=\"A modern outdoor patio with a wooden dining table and four chairs, set against a gray brick wall and next to a house with large glass windows.\" width=\"810\" height=\"608\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/DWR-Boutique-Experimential-Rental-Home-Wave-House-17-810x608.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/DWR-Boutique-Experimential-Rental-Home-Wave-House-17-800x600.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/DWR-Boutique-Experimential-Rental-Home-Wave-House-17-768x576.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/DWR-Boutique-Experimential-Rental-Home-Wave-House-17.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\" data-cfsrc=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/DWR-Boutique-Experimential-Rental-Home-Wave-House-17-810x608.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=576365\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-576365\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/DWR-Boutique-Experimential-Rental-Home-Wave-House-18-810x1013.jpg\" alt=\"A small patio with gravel ground, metal chairs, a wooden hot tub, palm trees, and a green brick wall, partially shaded by a metal roof.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1013\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/DWR-Boutique-Experimential-Rental-Home-Wave-House-18-810x1013.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/DWR-Boutique-Experimential-Rental-Home-Wave-House-18-800x1000.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/DWR-Boutique-Experimential-Rental-Home-Wave-House-18-768x960.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/DWR-Boutique-Experimential-Rental-Home-Wave-House-18-1229x1536.jpg 1229w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/DWR-Boutique-Experimential-Rental-Home-Wave-House-18.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\" data-cfsrc=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/DWR-Boutique-Experimential-Rental-Home-Wave-House-18-810x1013.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=576366\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-576366\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/DWR-Boutique-Experimential-Rental-Home-Wave-House-19-810x532.jpg\" alt=\"A metal bench sits on gravel under a slatted wooden structure in a modern, enclosed garden with desert plants and a painted brick wall.\" width=\"810\" height=\"532\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/DWR-Boutique-Experimential-Rental-Home-Wave-House-19-810x532.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/DWR-Boutique-Experimential-Rental-Home-Wave-House-19-800x525.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/DWR-Boutique-Experimential-Rental-Home-Wave-House-19-768x504.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/DWR-Boutique-Experimential-Rental-Home-Wave-House-19-385x252.jpg 385w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/DWR-Boutique-Experimential-Rental-Home-Wave-House-19.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\" data-cfsrc=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/DWR-Boutique-Experimential-Rental-Home-Wave-House-19-810x532.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=576367\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-576367\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/DWR-Boutique-Experimential-Rental-Home-Wave-House-20-810x456.jpg\" alt=\"Two modern, curved green outdoor chairs are placed on a gravel patio surrounded by desert plants, including cacti and palm trees, against a light-colored wall.\" width=\"810\" height=\"456\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/DWR-Boutique-Experimential-Rental-Home-Wave-House-20-810x456.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/DWR-Boutique-Experimential-Rental-Home-Wave-House-20-800x450.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/DWR-Boutique-Experimential-Rental-Home-Wave-House-20-768x432.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/DWR-Boutique-Experimential-Rental-Home-Wave-House-20-600x337.jpg 600w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/DWR-Boutique-Experimential-Rental-Home-Wave-House-20.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\" data-cfsrc=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/DWR-Boutique-Experimential-Rental-Home-Wave-House-20-810x456.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eWhether you’re an architecture enthusiast, a design professional, or simply a traveler looking for inspiration, this one-of-a-kind destination offers a glimpse into the possibilities of modern living – rooted in history, redefined by creativity.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=576368\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-576368\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/DWR-Boutique-Experimential-Rental-Home-Wave-House-21-810x532.jpg\" alt=\"A modern, flat-roofed house with a curved overhang, surrounded by desert plants and palm trees, set against a mountainous backdrop at sunset.\" width=\"810\" height=\"532\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/DWR-Boutique-Experimential-Rental-Home-Wave-House-21-810x532.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/DWR-Boutique-Experimential-Rental-Home-Wave-House-21-800x525.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/DWR-Boutique-Experimential-Rental-Home-Wave-House-21-768x504.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/DWR-Boutique-Experimential-Rental-Home-Wave-House-21-385x252.jpg 385w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/DWR-Boutique-Experimential-Rental-Home-Wave-House-21.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\" data-cfsrc=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/DWR-Boutique-Experimential-Rental-Home-Wave-House-21-810x532.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eBookings for the \u003ca href=\"https://boutique-homes.com/property/the-desert-wave\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener external noreferrer\" data-wpel-link=\"external\"\u003eDWR x Boutique rental\u003c/a\u003e are now open until August 31, 2025, and all furnishings featured in the space are available for purchase at \u003ca href=\"https://www.dwr.com/paul-smith-maharam?lang=en_US\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener external noreferrer\" data-wpel-link=\"external\"\u003edwr.com\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cem\u003ePhotography courtesy of DWR.\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n                        \n                                                    \u003cdiv\u003e\n                                \u003cdiv\u003e\n                                    \u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2021/11/Caroline-Williamson-100x100.jpg\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2021/11/Caroline-Williamson.jpg 2x\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" alt=\"\" data-cfsrc=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2021/11/Caroline-Williamson-100x100.jpg\"/\u003e                                    \u003c/p\u003e\n                                \u003c/div\u003e\n\n                                \u003cdiv\u003e\n                                    \u003cp\u003eCaroline Williamson is Editor-in-Chief of Design Milk. She has a BFA in photography from SCAD and can usually be found searching for vintage wares, doing New York Times crossword puzzles in pen, or reworking playlists on Spotify.\u003c/p\u003e\n                                    \n                                \u003c/div\u003e\n                            \u003c/div\u003e\n                                            \u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
